Package: hound
Type: Package
Title: A simple package to help journalists and other storytellers produce reproducible code and show their work.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: John D. Harden
Maintainer: John D. Harden <jdhardenjr@gmail.com>
Description: An ongoing project that compiles the most commonly used calculations used by
    journalist to avoid errors in data analysis. The goal of this project is to help
    writers avoid mistakes when using data. 
License: 
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: tidyverse